summary: I know you've said before that you read y/n as Beka. Was that confusing to write or read since those are two separate characters...
question: I know you've said before that you read y/n as Beka. Was that confusing to write or read since those are two separate characters in this fic?
answer:
OMG you have no idea!

In chapter 1, when Beka and Y/N are talking in the kitchen… my head exploded. I said to Bill… I just wrote “Beka turned her back on Beka and Beka sighed” I … Instant migraine! lol

After a while, i was trying to use another name as Y/N, but I’m conditioned really to see it as Beka, so it was very difficult. One scene towards the end, I had left it for a while and came back to finish, and accidentally really wrote “Y/N” for like 4 paragraphs before I realized what I was doing. 

It was a very interesting experience.

Taehyung’s Alphabets - H ~ Hwarang

Taehyung has always mentioned how he is passionate about acting and he started his journey as an actor as Hansung! The way he embodied his character was so amazing to watch! Hwarang also gave us the beautiful friendship between Tae and his Hwarang hyungs and let’s not forget Taejin’s Even If I Die It’s You which even now is one of my favourite songs!
